Program: Outlook
Title: Father Alec Reid and ETA
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrw7
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at the Basque separatist movement and an interview with Irish priest Alec Reid who is behind ETA's ceasefire. Also, vigango, memorial statues erected by the Mijikenda being stolen as art treasure from Kenya; selective mutism in children. Presenter: Heather Payton.